<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>future module on Hi, I'm Vimiix</title><link>https://www.vimiix.com/tags/future-module/</link><description>Recent content in future module on Hi, I'm Vimiix</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>cn-zh</language><copyright>Copyright (c) 2017-2021, Vimiix Yao; All rights reserved</copyright><lastBuildDate>Fri, 12 May 2017 14:55:03 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.vimiix.com/tags/future-module/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Python-from __future__ import print_function</title><link>https://www.vimiix.com/posts/2017-05-12-print-function/</link><pubDate>Fri, 12 May 2017 14:55:03 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.vimiix.com/posts/2017-05-12-print-function/</guid><description>&lt;p>Python 提供了**__future__**模块，把下一个新版本的特性导入到当前版本，于是我们就可以在当前版本中测试一些新版本的特性&lt;/p>
&lt;p>在 python2.x 的环境是使用下面语句，则第二句语法检查通过，第三句语法检查失败&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-Python" data-lang="Python"> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">from&lt;/span> __future__ &lt;span style="color:#f92672">import&lt;/span> print_function
&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">print&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;good&amp;#39;&lt;/span>) &lt;span style="color:#75715e">#可以通过执行&lt;/span>
&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">print&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;bad&amp;#39;&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#75715e">#语法错误&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>